caption: Excellent place for our babies! Definitely recommend this small park/play area

Sort of surreal visit. We stopped at this park after walking all day just to rest about a week into the Russian invasion. Did not previously know about the church or writer this is dedicated to. While we there, workers were loading a van with donations for displaced Ukrainians. There were also many cars driving by in protest as well. Beautiful park and lovely people from the church.
Nice local spot to have our lunch and refresh after our visit to the nearby Louvre Museum. Adjacent to the church, many benches to chose from and decent shade.
